屋企人永遠都係正常人果group 啦"},{"pid":"5f00c7f7c2e37250d213e0ae5ff8e73116aa1b6a","tid":115883,"uid":63462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T03:48:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該禁止會員繼續鳩up</blockquote><br />\n繁忙時間大幅加廢老票價係絕對有討論空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOk 咁就要正式將人分上中等<br />\n上等如正常人有手有腳60樓下就申請個正常人證 咩時間都搭得<br />\n傷殘就無乜人權既 只能早上八點前晚上八點後搭車<br />\n老人同婦女小朋友太易受傷要人照顧同上述人等一樣<br />\n<br />\n希望你同你屋企人永遠都係正常人果group 啦</blockquote><br />\n大撚把地方都將票價分off-peak hour啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ff3ad69ddf4dbf37f036f1bcf14e472720b848","tid":115883,"uid":63462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T03:52:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都想開呢個post<br />\n其實取消繁忙時間2蚊優惠就得<br />\n<br />\n佢老味我日日放工已經鳩閪咁攰啦<br />\n佢地就專登收工時間坐巴士返屋企<br />\n巴士又多人，企都冇得企咁滯<br />\n<br />\n真係好撚乞人憎</blockquote><br />\n班廢老橫掂都係等死搭4點車同6點車都冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSend曬去比特狗候選人囉</blockquote><br />\n廢老係民建聯鐵票呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家攪清楚先，老人家好可能已經係香港活咗幾十年，為社會服務咗大半生。今日佢哋受尊重，係應該。重點係今日大家見到嘅老人家係咪真係個個都為香港付出過？</blockquote><br />\n佢後生果時你畀少蚊佢都唔做呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到佢地後生做義工咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3351e329668ec643bd273c20951fc5a68c1b28","tid":115883,"uid":63462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e915f1984180b91b6ba50a8ab495bf9fe96aac","tid":115883,"uid":42048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:13:40.000Z","msg":"繁忙時間收返正價啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f49c9625adffdb03bc7391d045640215